Description:
ARALUEN
First time offered for sale. One continuously family owned apartment since c1935 in South Yarras most prestigious riverside locale. Enviably positioned just two doors from the Royal Botanic Gardens with spectacular river views, this generously proportioned, light filled apartment of approx. 140 sqm offers wonderful living spaces and three bedroom accommodation in comfortable order, yet offering improvement potential.
Comprising:
- Security entrance to large entrance hall
- Large living room overlooking the Yarra river
- Master bedroom with balcony to river
- Second double bedroom also offers river views
- Separate formal dining room overlooking the Royal Botanic Gardens and Government House
- Third double bedroom
- Large family bathroom
- Well appointed kitchen
- Rear door with access to communal garden
- Lock up garage, extra car space and separate laundry all on title
- One of only 4 apartments
- Walking distance to CBD, St Kilda Road, Toorak Road shopping and one of the most desirable offerings in recent times.
Insights: 3/7 Alexandra Avenue, South Yarra VIC 3141 was last sold in 2019 and 49 other 3 bedroom unit in South Yarra have recently been sold.

Description:
North Facing Two Bedroom in Leafy Locale
From an elevated ground floor position, in a secure boutique development of just eighteen with undercover off street parking and storage on title, this attractive north facing apartment captures a leafy outlook and abundant natural light. Classic charm is balanced by smart interior updates including a stunning kitchen transformation providing the jewel in the crown of a highly functional floorplan with balcony. Two spacious, sunny bedrooms with built in robes are serviced by a large bathroom featuring washing machine facilities plus a separate powder room. An impressive open plan kitchen (DW) with island bench flows to the lounge/dining fitted with reverse cycle heating/cooling and a balcony. Representing an excellent opportunity for those seeking a gorgeous apartment in a central South Yarra location, surrounded by lifestyle amenities such as public transport, shops, cafes and restaurants, Como Park, Rockley Gardens and the Yarra River.

Description:
Position perfect!
FOR AN INSPECTION THAT SUITS YOUR TIME CONTACT US DIRECTLY
Privately positioned in a timeless Mid-Century Modern building, this ultra-roomy 1 bedroom apartment classically combines space, serenity and sunlit style.
Enjoy a separate kitchen with stainless-steel appliances plus dishwasher, window-walled living and dining, and a cosy, first-floor balcony capturing morning sun.
Freshly painted, special features include sleek timber flooring, high ceilings, off-street parking, and a sparkling bathroom with a bath and laundry facilities.
* 1 large and light, north-facing bedroom with BIR and wall-to-wall windows
* Panel heating
* Twin block-out roller blinds over openable windows
* Secure entrance
* Boutique block of just 15
Moments from Chapel Street and Hawksburn rail and retail in a peaceful pocket, investors can set and forget, while market entrants can purchase with confidence.
For more information, please contact Andrew McCalman today.

Description:
Bespoke South Yarra Penthouse Residence
Expressions of Interest Closing Tuesday 30th April, 2019 at 4pm
Drenched in natural light and impeccably appointed throughout, this sublime Sue Carr designed penthouse caters for luxurious contemporary living in the heart of blue-chip South Yarra.
Sophisticated and spacious, this marvellous residence features a cutting edge designer kitchen with porcelain bench tops, top of the line Gaggenau appliances, scullery and 2 pac finishes, alongside a vast North-facing living and dining domain with fireplace. An expansive wraparound terrace - complete with retractable awnings and external retractable louvres - provide the perfect sunny backdrop for seamless alfresco entertaining while three superb bedrooms deliver first class accommodation. A large study/fourth bedroom (currently used as an entertainment room), two lavish ensuites, and a third central bathroom plus separate laundry complete the impressive floorplan.
The stylish home also boasts soaring ceilings, electric block-out blinds and retractable sheers, LED lighting and individual heating/cooling. Two side-by-side basement car parks and a generous storage unit accompany this rare offering.
Offering a lifestyle of absolute ease and convenience, the property is set in a secure premium development just metres from cafés and shops, and a stones throw from Fawkner Park and the Royal Botanic Gardens.

Description:
Affordable & Convenient South Yarra living!
Well insulated from the hustle and bustle of the South Yarra lifestyle, this bright and secure home offers the appeal of a modern building in a small low rise development. This apartment features an open plan living/dining leading out to a private balcony to entertain. Kitchen with ample storage, stone bench tops & DW, double bedroom with multiple BIRs, bathroom with shower over bath & laundry facilities. Part of a secure block with elevator, home features ducted heating & cooling, secure basement undercover car parking and finally walk outside your private oasis to take advantage of the terrific lifestyle that South Yarra offers. A short walk to countless cafes, trams and train station at one end of Darling Street or take a stroll to the Royal Botanic Gardens for a run around the Tan, through the gardens or along the Yarra river. A unique opportunity to get into South Yarra and the perfect time to take advantage of the newly accessible First Home buyer savings.

Description:
Spectacular Is Its Middle Name!
An exclusive 2-bedroom apartment packed with features from top to bottom, you'll be in awe from the moment you step inside.
Only 3 years old, this near-new apartment features an open plan lounge, dining and kitchen area with a terrace. The bathroom is fully tiled, and the kitchen boasts beautiful stainless steel Miele appliances, and a stone bench top.
Other fantastic highlights include split system heating and cooling, built-in-robes in the bedrooms, a European laundry, and timber flooring.
Situated in the renowned Lucia building by Elenberg Fraser, you're presented with resort-style facilities including an infinity pool, a gym, a spa, a sauna and landscaped gardens.
Located in the heart of South Yarra, you are within walking distance to Chapel Street, Toorak Road, South Yarra Station, the Como Centre, Jam Factory, premium schools, and Melbourne's elite retail outlets. What more could you ask for?!
Perfect for young couples and investors alike, contact Paul Torok on 0490815564 today!

Description:
Lock Up and Leave Lifestyle in Blue Chip Position
Providing a low maintenance lock-up and leave lifestyle in an unbeatable blue-chip position close to South Yarra Station, trams, Chapel Street and Toorak Road restaurants, cafes and boutique shops, the Yarra River bike paths and the Royal Botanic Gardens, this sleek fourth level apartment is situated within a secure development boasting lift access and a communal rooftop garden and BBQ. With a basement carspace on title, intercom entrance and a balcony as just some of the highlights, the apartment comprises of an open plan kitchen (DW) and lounge, bedroom with mirrored built in robes and a spacious bathroom with an oversized shower. Concealed laundry facilities, heating/cooling and an intercom entrance add to the value, creating a sensational entry level opportunity into the highly sought after South Yarra market.

Description:
LIGHT FILLED LIFESTYLE LIVING IN THE DESIRABLE DOMAIN PRECINCT
Prestigiously positioned between Fawkner Park and the Royal Botanic Gardens, you couldn't pick a better place to set up home or invest than in this prized parkland precinct.
Presenting a truly exciting and ultra-convenient lifestyle with the huge advantage of an over-sized lock-up garage with plenty of storage space, this apartment features a remarkably roomy living and dining room, refurbished kitchen with stainless-steel oven and gas cooktop, dishwasher and meals area, two extra-large bedrooms with generous built-in robes and an updated bathroom with a shower above the bath tub and washing machine taps.
A relaxing balcony enjoys wonderful views across green gardens towards the pristine boom style historical terrace houses lining the keenly sought-after street.
Floorboards, floor-to-ceiling cupboards in the hallway, new bedroom carpets and large light-loving picture windows further complement this ready-to-enjoy package, which is within walking distance to tram routes, South Yarra Station, the Yarra River and Toorak Road's swish boutiques, art galleries, bars, retail outlets and some of Melbourne's best restaurants and cafes.

Description:
The Ultimate Warehouse Conversion
The inspired architect designed conversion of this former cotton mill has resulted in an absolutely breathtaking inner urban sanctuary literally metres from Toorak Rd and Chapel St's retail and restaurant precincts, Como Cinemas, trams and the Yarra River. The 5 commercial lift connected levels, culminating in a resort style rooftop garden with swim-spa, showcases state of the art design, luxury and quality throughout.
Bathed in light from both ends, the sensational living and dining areas featuring dark Tasmanian oak floors, designer pendant lights and an ethanol fireplace surrounded by stacked stone are either side of a sublime commercial grade Miele kitchen boasting stone benches. The beautiful main bedroom with lavish Limestone en-suite and walk in robe sets a benchmark in opulence that is matched by three additional double bedrooms with built in robes and Limestone en-suites, a fitted study and internal light-well. The spectacular rooftop entertaining precinct comprises a swim spa with waterfall, second spa and large Bluestone al fresco terrace with BBQ and kitchenette appointed with bar fridge, freezer, sink and wok burner.
Comprehensively finished to the highest standards, this impressive domain also includes alarm, heating/cooling, Bose audio inside and out, remote binds, dumb waiter, Euro-laundry, drying room, ample storage, work-shop and internally accessed 3-car garage.

Stylish, spacious & Perfectly positioned in the heart of cosmopolitan South Yarra, this exceptionally appointed one-bedroom apartment in the sleek SKY2 complex, offers residents the very best in design & convenience with contemporary inner-city living. Conveniently located only footsteps away from Toorak Roads high end bars & restaurants, Chapel Streets famous shopping precinct & cosmopolitan nightlife, exclusive fashionable boutiques, the iconic Prahran Market & South Yarra Station. This Apartment embraces the peaceful ambiance of designer living in perfect proximity to the round-the-clock vibrancy and lifestyle allure of South Yarra.
